# Stdlib + resolved deps: `lib/` is populated by `cyrius deps` from
# cyrius.cyml [deps] (stdlib + sakshi), matching patra/sigil — it is
# NOT vendored. A stale 5.7.x copy was tracked through 0.3.0; at 0.4.0
# it is untracked (run `git rm -r --cached lib/` once to drop it).
/lib/
